_sText:
Maximum Players: 50

Including:

- 5 Large rooms, one huge with four teleporters and one little barricade room.
- 7+ different spots to hide, some of them needs teamwork.
- Teleporters.
- A Room full of water! - Be careful, if you dont get to a safe place, you might die slowly.
- Breakable Windows, almost every window is breakable.
- One little ''secret'' room
- In the fourth floor, there's some platform you can jump from to another.

- There may be some bugs in this map, but it does'nt affect your gameplay much.

Enjoy!
